Name: Swift of Wind VI
Desc:
[Fusion Skill] Mir, while using Dragon Swift, responds to Evan's magic and shoots sharp wind blades by agitating air currents. Swift of Wind does not cause you to take damage even when attacking enemies in the Damage Reflection Status.
This skill is activated when Evan casts Circle of Wind while Mir is using Dragon Swift.
Required Skill: Swift of Wind Lv. 20 or higher

Desc.Old:
